    "summary": {
      "value": "Gain benefits for consecutive attacks with brawling weapons."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Fury </strong>and <strong>Weaponmaster</strong>.</p></blockquote><p>When you perform a <strong>melee </strong>attack using a weapon that belongs to the <strong>brawling </strong>Category,<strong> if you have no martial armor and no shields equipped</strong>, you gain <strong>1 Bravery Point</strong>.</p><p>As long as you have no <strong>martial armor</strong> and no <strong>shields</strong> equipped, your <strong>melee</strong> attacks with <strong>brawling</strong> weapons deal extra damage equal to <strong>【2 + your current Bravery Points】</strong>.</p><p>At the end of each scene, <strong>or </strong>if you have <strong>5 or more Bravery Points</strong> at the end of your turn, you lose all accumulated Bravery Points. Then, if you lost at least 1 point this way, you recover 10 Hit Points <strong>and</strong> 10 Mind Points</p><hr /><ul><li><p><strong>Resource:</strong> @PROGRESS[rising-tide update 1]{Advance Bravery Point}, or @PROGRESS[rising-tide reset]{Reset Bravery Point}</p></li><li><p><strong>You Recover:</strong> @GAIN[10 hp] and/or @GAIN[10 mp]</p></li></ul>",
